    "description": "这是完整游戏“Planet Crafter”的序幕。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >从敌对到宜居</h2><br>你被派往一个充满敌意的星球，任务是：让它适合人类居住。你必须生存，收集资源，建造基地和机器，以加热地球，创造一个有足够氧气的大气层，并最终对整个星球进行地球工程！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830840/extras/29d266513ab49288461f5db02a342d2b.poster.avif?t=1730825572\" width=606 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830840/extras/29d266513ab49288461f5db02a342d2b.webm?t=1730825572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830840/extras/29d266513ab49288461f5db02a342d2b.mp4?t=1730825572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >生存、收集、制作</h2>收集矿物和资源以生存。制作完成任务所需的所有工具。探索旧的坠毁船只和废墟，发现一个充满神秘色彩的星球。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 建立你自己的基地 </h2>你需要一个基地和各种各样的机器来让自己像在家里一样，并能够在这个星球上带来生命！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830840/extras/6a503ecebf7d68a99c271225a2fa9997.poster.avif?t=1730825572\" width=606 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830840/extras/6a503ecebf7d68a99c271225a2fa9997.webm?t=1730825572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830840/extras/6a503ecebf7d68a99c271225a2fa9997.mp4?t=1730825572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特点:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 性格口渴、氧气、温度、健康机制 </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 基地建设 </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 制作</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 开采矿石 </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 建造机器以产生大气压 </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 建造机器来加热地球 </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 创造一个有氧的生物圈 </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 在星球上创造生命！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830840/extras/061057b74653a3bea13a28f7190006fc.poster.avif?t=1730825572\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830840/extras/061057b74653a3bea13a28f7190006fc.webm?t=1730825572\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1830840/extras/061057b74653a3bea13a28f7190006fc.mp4?t=1730825572\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
